description: I have lived many experiences that if I had not taken the risk of accepting chaos I could never have lived, I have met beautiful people inside and out thanks to deciding to take the risk of accepting chaos and get out of my sense of calm, life becomes interesting when you accept that chaos puts you in chaotic situations, only then can you really enjoy the wonders of being alive and not just being in asymptomatic agony with a totally disposable end.
